<div id="review_3039776582" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3039776582" />
    <a title="RJ - Slayer of Trolls" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/131730-rj---slayer-of-trolls"><img alt="RJ - Slayer of Trolls" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1644082981p2/131730.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3039776582?book_show_action=true">Apr 07, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="RJ - Slayer of Trolls" class="user" itemprop="url" name="RJ - Slayer of Trolls" href="/user/show/131730-rj---slayer-of-trolls">RJ - Slayer of Trolls</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was ok"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was ok</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780060736309" href="/book/show/1533442.By_the_River_Piedra_I_Sat_Down_and_Wept">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3039776582" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2813417563715943102">Childhood friends meet again as young adults and explore concepts of love, faith, commitment, spirituality, and religion, specifically Catholicism. The narrative never gets deep enough to inspire serious thought or discussion but in 180 double-spaced pages of large print it makes a nice snack for a neighborhood book club. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


